➜一言不合就噼叉，也只有杨天真了
http://www.sohu.com/a/412171528_255135	55672
<p class="ql-align-justify">没错，就是<strong>杨天真！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>她在《脱口秀大会》现场一言不合就噼叉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">真是个柔软的胖子，不是，雷厉风行的女企业家呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200808/aec22e6478434a7fb0b530eb4b80683a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那哆啦A梦一般的小圆手，紧紧握着话筒，站在台上一脸真诚地说：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>I have a dream</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200808/e4f170c1d0184b9d9303e41c0a91fe68.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200808/1b54d666d465446b886cbfed27a8b88e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
